@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rxrths(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = wp.abs((v1 / (v0 + 0.35 - v0 + 0.95)))
    tmp = ((v0 + (tmp + 0.90 + v1 + 0.47)) + wp.abs((v1 + 0.19 - v0 + 0.62)))
    v2 = tmp
    v1 = wp.exp(0.89)
    v2 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.79) + v1) + v2)
    data[tid] = v0
